```

```

Output

```
{"32-GGA":3}
```

## Algorithm
- Example string
```
'GAACATCATGT'
```

- Split string by length 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10 and shift index by length
```
["GAG", "GCA", "TCA", "TCA", "TCA", "TCA", "TTG", "AGG", "CAT", "CAT", "CAT", "CAT", "CAT", "TGC", "GGC", "ATC", "ATC", "ATC", "ATC", "ATT", "GCC", "GAGG", "CATC", "ATCA", "TCAT", "CATT", "AGGC", "ATCA", "TCAT", "CATC", "ATTG", "GGCA", "TCAT", "CATC", "ATCA", "TTGC", "GCAT", "CATC", "ATCA", "TCAT", "TGCC", "GAGGC", "ATCAT", "CATCA", "TCATT", "AGGCA", "TCATC", "ATCAT", "CATTG", "GGCAT", "CATCA", "TCATC", "ATTGC", "GCATC", "ATCAT", "CATCA", "TTGCC", "CATCA", "TCATC", "ATCAT", "GAGGCA", "TCATCA", "TCATCA", "AGGCAT", "CATCAT", "CATCAT", "GGCATC", "ATCATC", "ATCATT", "GCATCA", "TCATCA", "TCATTG", "CATCAT", "CATCAT", "CATTGC", "ATCATC", "ATCATC", "ATTGCC", "GAGGCAT", "CATCATC", "ATCATTG", "AGGCATC", "ATCATCA", "TCATTGC", "GGCATCA", "TCATCAT", "CATTGCC", "GCATCAT", "CATCATC", "CATCATC", "ATCATCA", "ATCATCA", "TCATCAT", "TCATCAT", "CATCATT", "GAGGCATC", "ATCATCAT", "AGGCATCA", "TCATCATC", "GGCATCAT", …]
```

- Find duplicate of string
```
["TCA", "TCA", "TCA", "CAT", "CAT", "CAT", "CAT", "ATC", "ATC", "ATC", "TCATCA", "CATCAT", "CATCAT", "ATCATC", "CATCATC", "ATCATCA", "TCATCAT"]
```

- Count duplicate string in the array
```
{TCA: 4, CAT: 5, ATC: 4, TCATCA: 2, CATCAT: 3, …}
```

- Format output
```
{4-CAT: 5}
````
